LxsC&amp;pg=PA64\"><i>The Painter's Handbook: A Complete Reference</i> by Mark David Gottsegen, p. 64</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=DCN21wUqnS8C&amp;pg=PA28\"><i>Elizabeth Tolley, Oil Painter's Solution Book \u2013 Landscapes: Over 100 Answers to Your Oil Painting</i></a>. p.&#160;28<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-04-09</span></span>  &#8211; via Books.google.com.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Elizabeth+Tolley%2C+Oil+Painter%27s+Solution+Book+%E2%80%93+Landscapes%3A+Over+100+Answers+to+Your+Oil+Painting&amp;rft.pages=28&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DDCN21wUqnS8C%26pg%3DPA28&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGesso\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=o23u0SuRLxsC&amp;pg=PA321\"><i>The Painter's Handbook: A Complete Reference</i>, by Mark David Gottsegen. p. 321</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150603155459/https://books.google.com/books?id=o23u0SuRLxsC&amp;pg=PA321\">Archived</a> June 3, 2015, at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Michael Friel (2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books